message.en_US: Is that the source of wicked kittens?!
message.pt_BR: Essa é a fonte dos gatos perversos?!

message.zh_CN: 这就是邪猫出现的源头了？！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

これが邪悪な猫たちの
根源なのか？！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Indeed! Summoning evil black cats on poor villagers! This can't stand!!
message.pt_BR: De fato! Invocar gatos negros malignos contra pobres aldeões! Isso não pode ficar assim!!
message.de_DE: Allerdings! Böse schwarze Katzen auf arme Dorfbewohner hetzen! Ein unhaltbarer Zustand!!
message.zh_CN: 居然召唤邪恶的黑猫袭击无辜村民。不可容忍！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
その通り！邪悪な黒猫を召喚して
村人たちを苦しめているんだ！
ええい、もう我慢できない！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 그런가 봐! 불쌍한 마을 사람들에게 악마 같은 검은 고양이를 소환하다니. 참을 수 없어!!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 居然召喚邪惡的黑貓襲擊無辜村民。不可容忍！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Looks like those were the last of them.
message.pt_BR: Parece que esses foram os últimos.
message.de_DE: Sieht so aus, als wären das alle gewesen.
message.zh_CN: 看来这就是最后一只了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
message.ja_JP: これで終わりみたいだな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
message.zh_TW: 看來這就是最後一隻了。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]

なんだったんだろうな？<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/11/27]

message.de_DE: Was waren das bloß für Dinger?
message.zh_TW: 不過這些到底是什麼東西？<<A<<[CHANGED 2017/12/12]

message.en_US: Indeed! Were they really an extension of the power plant? Very mysterious!
message.pt_BR: De fato! Eles eram realmente uma extensão da usina de energia? Muito misterioso!
message.de_DE: Gute Frage! Waren das wirklich Ausläufer des Kraftwerks? Äußerst mysteriös!
message.zh_CN: 是啊！它们真的是发电站里弄出来的？真是奇怪！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ja_JP:
まったくだ！これは本当に
パワープラントから伸びてきた何かか？
不思議でならないな！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.ko_KR: 그러게! 그게 정말 발전소의 연장선이었을까? 정말 알 수 없군!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]
message.zh_TW: 是啊！它們真的是發電站裡弄出來的？真是奇怪！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/03/14]

message.en_US: Let's return to that K'tara girl for now.
